title: World Series question: Do you like Fox-TV's oily decison to pair Pete Rose with Alex Rodriguez?
text: World Series question: Do you like Fox-TV's oily decison to pair Pete Rose with Alex Rodriguez? Pete Rose Reinstatement Baseball Pete Rose will work as an in-studio analyst, along with his partner in baseball scandal, Alex Rodriguez, for Fox-TV during the World Series that is scheduled to begin on Tuesday night in Kansas City. Some folks aren't all that happy with this arrangement, but the Fox people are confident about one thing: Rose and Rodriguez should attract eyeballs. (Charlie Nye | The Associated Press)
